ple\n| [[red apple]] ({{taxlink|Syzygium ingens|species}})|road apple|[[rose apple]] ({{taxlink|Angophora costata|species}}; {{taxfmt|Syzygium|genus}} spp.)|rotten apple| {{vern|rosey apple aphid}} ({{taxlink|Dysaphia plantaginea|species}})\n| {{vern|sage-apple}}|[[sea apple]], [[sea-apple]]|seven-year apple|{{vern|sheld-apple}} ({{vern|shell-apple}})|[[she'll be apples]]; [[she's apples]]|snap apple|snow apple,snow-apple|{{vern|soap apple}} ({{taxlink|Chlorogalum pomeridianum|species}})|{{vern|soda apple}} ({{taxlink|Solanum aculeastrum|species}})|Sodom apple|sorb apple,sorb-apple|[[star apple]] ({{taxfmt|Chrysophyllum cainito|species}})|stocking-apple|{{vern|stone apple}} ({{taxfmt|Aegle marmelos|species}})|street apple|[[sugar apple]], [[sugar-apple]] ({{taxfmt|Annona squamosa|species}})|sweet apple|{{vern|swamp apple}} ({{taxlink|Annona glabra|species}})\n| table apple|[[taffy apple]] ([[toffee apple]])|the apple doesn't fall far from the tree|the apples on the other side of the wall are the sweetest|the [[Big Apple]]|the [[Little Apple]]|there are bad apples in every orchard,there's a rotten apple in every barrel|[[thorn apple]] ({{taxfmt|Datura stramonium|species}})|thorn-apple crystal|toffee apple| {{vern|tropical soda apple}} ({{taxlink|Solanum viarum|species}})\n| vi-apple|{{vern|vine apple}}\n| {{vern|water apple}} ({{taxlink|Syzygium aqueum|species}})|[[wax apple]] ({{taxfmt|Syzygium samarangense|species}})|Westbury apple|{{vern|wild balsam apple}}|wild custard apple|{{vern|wine apple}}|{{vern|winter apple}} ({{taxlink|Eremophila debilis|species}})|wise apple,wise-apple|{{vern|wolf apple}} ({{taxlink|Solanum lycocarpum|species}})|[[wood apple]] ({{taxfmt|Aegle marmelos|species}} etc.)|{{vern|woolly apple aphid}} ({{taxlink|Eriosoma lanigerum|species}})|worm in the apple\n| zombi apple}}\n\n====Descendants====\n{{topN-collapsible|3}}\n* {{desctree|srn|apra|unc=1}}\n* {{desc|abe|aples|bor=1}} {{qualifier|< {{m|en|apples}}}}\n* {{desc|ari|ápos|bor=1}} {{qual